value.0: Various gears control the locking mechanism of this metal-clad door.

This ostentatious statue is a grand figure of a humanoid man, towering over the chamber. It's carved from blackened stone, and looks as though it has been drenched in blood, leaving a mottled red pattern across its surface.

The symbol of Cyric is emblazoned on its chest, a dark sun surrounded in flame. It's eyes burn with eerie red fire, gazing balefully down upon those before it.
This old rubble might contain objects from times long past. You will have to search it thoroughly to be sure.
